Method for preparing purified for the crystal methamphetamine standard substance of forensic science illicit drugs inspection

Abstract
translated from Chinese

The invention discloses a method for purifying and preparing methamphetamine standard substances used in forensic drug detection, comprising the following steps: (1) detecting the purity of methamphetamine in seized methamphetamine samples, and selecting methamphetamine with a mass fraction greater than or equal to 70wt % of the seized methamphetamine samples are used as raw materials for purification and preparation of methamphetamine standard substances; (2) high performance liquid chromatography is utilized to prepare methamphetamine standard substances; the resulting methamphetamine has high purity and can be directly used as standard substances. The methamphetamine obtained by the preparation and purification method of the present invention is confirmed by nuclear magnetic resonance, liquid chromatography-tandem mass spectrometry, and infrared spectrum analysis, and its purity is determined by liquid chromatography and gas chromatography, and the chromatographic non-responsive impurities are measured; According to the requirements for the development of reference materials, the estimation of its stability, uniformity, fixed value, and total uncertainty all meet the relevant regulations and meet the expected indicators.

Description
translated from Chinese

用于法庭科学毒品检测的甲基苯丙胺标准物质的纯化制备 方法Purification and preparation of methamphetamine standard substances for forensic drug testing method

技术领域technical field

本发明涉及法庭科学毒品检测。更具体地，涉及一种用于法庭科学毒品检测的甲基苯丙胺标准物质的纯化制备方法。The present invention relates to forensic science drug testing. More specifically, it relates to a method for purifying and preparing methamphetamine standard substances used in forensic drug detection.

背景技术Background technique

目前，日趋严重的毒品问题已成为全球性的灾难。毒品的泛滥直接危害人民的身心健康，并给经济发展和社会进步带来巨大威胁。因此，建立法庭科学毒品检测量值溯源体系，提高毒品成份量测量技术，保证测量结果的可靠性和可比性，建立测量数据的共享与互认，为法庭提供准确可靠的证据，已成为世界各国毒品鉴定机构普遍关注的问题。At present, the increasingly serious drug problem has become a global disaster. The proliferation of drugs directly endangers people's physical and mental health, and poses a huge threat to economic development and social progress. Therefore, establishing a forensic scientific drug detection quantity traceability system, improving the measurement technology of drug components, ensuring the reliability and comparability of measurement results, establishing the sharing and mutual recognition of measurement data, and providing accurate and reliable evidence for courts has become a national standard in the world. A general concern of drug identification agencies.

毒品成份量测量技术及溯源性保障是一个有机的整体，是核心测量能力在法庭科学毒品成份量测量领域的重要体现。标准物质是贯穿于这个整体的骨架，是量值的载体，是毒品成份量溯源体系的关键要素，是保证测量结果在时间和空间上的准确性和可比性的重要基础，是实现有效测量即准确、可比、可溯源测量的根本保证。Drug composition measurement technology and traceability guarantee are an organic whole, which is an important embodiment of core measurement capabilities in the field of forensic drug composition measurement. The reference material is the skeleton that runs through the whole, the carrier of the quantity value, the key element of the traceability system of drug ingredients, the important basis for ensuring the accuracy and comparability of the measurement results in time and space, and the realization of effective measurement that is The fundamental guarantee for accurate, comparable and traceable measurements.

欧美等国家技术先进的毒品检测实验室大多采用Sigma等公司生产的国际上公认的标准物质，但在我国只能依赖进口的标准物质，量少价高，有许多还不能向中国提供。目前国内毒品分析中使用的“对照品”不仅种类极为有限，而且普遍缺乏完善的结构鉴定、纯度测定、均匀性和稳定性等相应的技术指标。这些都给涉毒案件检测带来一定的不确定性，直接影响到定量结果的准确性。而且，国内毒品标准物质的匮乏，已经成为制约我国实现法庭科学毒品检测化学测量方法标准化、测量结果的溯源和互认的主要障碍。因此，能够制备出用于法庭科学毒品检测的毒品标准物质已经成为我国毒品研究领域亟需解决的问题。Most of the advanced drug testing laboratories in Europe and the United States use internationally recognized reference materials produced by companies such as Sigma, but in my country we can only rely on imported reference materials, which are small in quantity and high in price, and many of them cannot be provided to China. At present, the types of "reference substances" used in domestic drug analysis are not only extremely limited, but also generally lack corresponding technical indicators such as perfect structure identification, purity determination, uniformity and stability. All of these bring certain uncertainties to the detection of drug-related cases and directly affect the accuracy of quantitative results. Moreover, the lack of domestic drug standard substances has become a major obstacle restricting my country from realizing the standardization of forensic drug detection chemical measurement methods, traceability and mutual recognition of measurement results. Therefore, the ability to prepare drug reference substances for forensic drug detection has become an urgent problem in the field of drug research in my country.

甲基苯丙胺又称甲基安非他明、冰毒、去氧麻黄素、脱氧麻黄碱。英文通用名称：Methamphetamine hydrochloride，化学名称：1-苯基-2-甲氨基丙烷，Chemical Name：Dimethylphenylethylamine hydrochloride，甲基苯丙胺盐酸盐分子式：CHN·HCl，分子量：185.70(anhyd.)，CA登记号：51-57-0结构式为：Methamphetamine is also known as methamphetamine, methamphetamine, methamphetamine, methamphetamine. English common name: Methamphetamine hydrochloride, chemical name: 1-phenyl-2-methylaminopropane, Chemical Name: Dimethylphenylethylamine hydrochloride, methamphetamine hydrochloride molecular formula: C 10 H 15 N HCl, molecular weight: 185.70 (anhyd.) , CA registration number: 51-57-0 The structural formula is:

理化性质：微带苦味，是一种无色片状结晶，熔点172℃～174℃，易溶于水(50mg/mL)、乙醇、不溶于乙醚，游离碱有氨臭。由于甲基苯丙胺分子中存在一个手性碳原子，因此甲基苯丙胺又分为左旋光学异构体和右旋光学异构体，二者等量混合物形成外消旋体。光学结构不同，其药性效果有很大差异，根据文献，右旋甲基苯丙胺比左旋甲基苯丙胺高几倍。Physical and chemical properties: slightly bitter taste, is a colorless flaky crystal, melting point 172 ℃ ~ 174 ℃, soluble in water (50mg/mL), ethanol, insoluble in ether, free base has ammonia odor. Due to the presence of a chiral carbon atom in the methamphetamine molecule, methamphetamine is further divided into a left-handed optical isomer and a right-handed optical isomer, and an equal mixture of the two forms a racemate. The optical structure is different, and its medicinal effect is very different. According to the literature, D-methamphetamine is several times higher than L-methamphetamine.

发明内容Contents of the invention

本发明的目的在于提供一种用于法庭科学毒品检测的甲基苯丙胺标准物质的纯化制备方法。The object of the present invention is to provide a kind of method for the purification and preparation of methamphetamine standard substance used for forensic science drug detection.

为达到上述目的，本发明采用下述技术方案：To achieve the above object, the present invention adopts the following technical solutions:

用于法庭科学毒品检测的甲基苯丙胺标准物质的纯化制备方法，包括如下步骤：The preparation method for the purification of the methamphetamine standard substance that is used for forensic science drug detection comprises the steps:

(1)检测缴获甲基苯丙胺样品中甲基苯丙胺的纯度，选择甲基苯丙胺质量分数大于或等于70wt％的缴获甲基苯丙胺样品作为纯化制备甲基苯丙胺标准物质的原料；(1) detect and seize the purity of methamphetamine in the methamphetamine sample, select the methamphetamine mass fraction greater than or equal to 70wt% and seize the methamphetamine sample as the raw material for purification and preparation of methamphetamine standard substance;

(2)利用高效液相色谱制备甲基苯丙胺标准物质。(2) Utilize high-performance liquid chromatography to prepare methamphetamine standard substance.

上述用于法庭科学毒品检测的甲基苯丙胺标准物质的纯化制备方法，在步骤(1)中，包括如下步骤：The above-mentioned purification preparation method for the methamphetamine standard substance that is used for forensic science drug detection, in step (1), comprises the following steps:

(1.1)样品溶液的制备：称取1mg甲基苯丙胺样品溶于1mL甲醇中，配成质量体积浓度为1mg/mL甲基苯丙胺样品溶液用于高效液相色谱分析，使用前，样品溶液经过0.45μm微孔滤膜过滤。(1.1) Preparation of sample solution: Weigh 1 mg of methamphetamine sample and dissolve it in 1 mL of methanol to form a mass volume concentration of 1 mg/mL methamphetamine sample solution for HPLC analysis. Before use, the sample solution is subjected to 0.45 μm microporous membrane filtration.

(1.2)确定液相色谱条件：色谱柱为Shim-pack HRC-ODS柱(250mm×4.6mm I.D.，5μm)；流动相为甲醇：0.05％三氟乙酸/水＝25:75，等度洗脱；紫外检测波长220nm；流速1.0mL/min；柱温为室温；(1.2) Determine the liquid chromatography conditions: the chromatographic column is a Shim-pack HRC-ODS column (250mm×4.6mm I.D., 5 μm); the mobile phase is methanol: 0.05% trifluoroacetic acid/water=25:75, isocratic elution ; UV detection wavelength 220nm; flow rate 1.0mL/min; column temperature is room temperature;

(1.3)计算标准曲线的回归方程及确定线性范围：用色谱甲醇逐级稀释市售1.0mg/mL甲基苯丙胺甲醇溶液，配制成浓度分别为1.0,0.5,0.1,0.05,0.01,0.005,0.001mg/mL的甲基苯丙胺标准溶液，按步骤(1.2)中选定的色谱条件测定，每个浓度重复3次，以平均值计算，记录甲基苯丙胺色谱峰面积，以标准品的进样浓度(μg/mL)为横坐标，色谱峰面积值为纵坐标作图，并计算标准曲线的回归方程，标准曲线的回归方程为：Y＝1930+5×10C，R＝1.0000；确定线性范围：甲基苯丙胺在0.001～1mg/mL的范围内线性关系良好；(1.3) Calculate the regression equation of the standard curve and determine the linear range: dilute the commercially available 1.0 mg/mL methamphetamine methanol solution step by step with chromatographic methanol, and prepare the concentrations as 1.0, 0.5, 0.1, 0.05, 0.01, 0.005, 0.001 The methamphetamine standard solution of mg/mL is determined by the chromatographic conditions selected in step (1.2), each concentration is repeated 3 times, calculated as the average value, and the methamphetamine chromatographic peak area is recorded, and the injection concentration of the standard (μg/mL) is the abscissa, and the chromatographic peak area value is plotted on the ordinate, and the regression equation of the standard curve is calculated. The regression equation of the standard curve is: Y=1930+5×10 6 C, R 2 =1.0000; determine Linear range: methamphetamine has a good linear relationship within the range of 0.001-1mg/mL;

(1.4)准确称取甲基苯丙胺白色晶体样品10mg于10mL容量瓶中，用色谱甲醇定容并混匀，配成质量浓度为1mg/mL的样品溶液；取该溶液经0.45μm微孔滤膜过滤后进行HPLC分析，连续测定3次，记录甲基苯丙胺峰面积并计算其平均值，按峰面积外标法计算样品中的甲基苯丙胺含量。(1.4) Accurately weigh 10 mg of methamphetamine white crystal sample in a 10 mL volumetric flask, dilute to volume with chromatographic methanol and mix well to prepare a sample solution with a mass concentration of 1 mg/mL; take the solution and pass it through a 0.45 μm microporous membrane After filtration, carry out HPLC analysis, measure 3 times continuously, record methamphetamine peak area and calculate its average value, calculate the content of methamphetamine in the sample according to peak area external standard method.

上述用于法庭科学毒品检测的甲基苯丙胺标准物质的纯化制备方法，在步骤(2)中，包括如下步骤：The above-mentioned purification preparation method for the methamphetamine standard substance that is used for forensic science drug detection, in step (2), comprises the following steps:

(2.1)样品溶液的制备：640mg甲基苯丙胺样品置于2mL容量瓶中，加入甲醇/水(体积比为1:1)至刻度线，超声5min，至样品全部溶解，配制成320mg/mL甲基苯丙胺样品溶液用于制备型高效液相色谱分离制备甲基苯丙胺标准品。使用前样品溶液经过0.45μm微孔滤膜过滤；(2.1) Preparation of sample solution: 640mg methamphetamine sample was placed in a 2mL volumetric flask, methanol/water (volume ratio 1:1) was added to the scale line, ultrasonicated for 5min until the sample was completely dissolved, and prepared into 320mg/mL formazan The sample solution of methamphetamine was used for preparative high performance liquid chromatography to prepare methamphetamine standard. Before use, the sample solution was filtered through a 0.45 μm microporous membrane;

(2.2)确定液相色谱条件：色谱柱为Shim-pack PRC-ODS(H)制备柱(250mm×20mmI.D.，5μm)；流动相为甲醇：水＝5:95，并将甲醇和水充分混匀脱气后使用，等度洗脱；紫外检测波长220nm；流速10mL/min；上样量160μL；柱温为室温；收集信号阈值高于75mAu范围内的馏分；(2.2) Determine the liquid chromatography conditions: the chromatographic column is a Shim-pack PRC-ODS (H) preparative column (250mm × 20mmI.D., 5 μm); the mobile phase is methanol: water=5:95, and methanol and water Use after fully mixing and degassing, isocratic elution; UV detection wavelength 220nm; flow rate 10mL/min; sample loading 160μL; column temperature at room temperature; collect fractions with a signal threshold higher than 75mAu;

(2.3)将收集到的馏分经减压旋蒸后得到无色透明晶体，用蒸馏水溶解并调节溶液pH为12；加入正己烷，萃取2次，每次萃取时水相与有机相体积比为1：1，合并有机相，往有机相中加入有机相体积的二分之一的水，逐滴滴加0.01NHCl溶液直至溶液pH为4-5，旋转蒸发去除正己烷，剩余水相经过冷冻干燥或旋转蒸发获得最终制备产物甲基苯丙胺盐酸盐晶体，置于真空干燥箱室温下干燥。(2.3) The collected cuts are obtained by rotary evaporation under reduced pressure to obtain colorless transparent crystals, which are dissolved in distilled water and adjusted to a pH of 12; add n-hexane and extract 2 times, and the volume ratio of the aqueous phase to the organic phase during each extraction is 1:1, combine the organic phase, add 1/2 of the volume of the organic phase to the organic phase, add 0.01N HCl solution drop by drop until the pH of the solution is 4-5, remove n-hexane by rotary evaporation, and freeze the remaining water phase Drying or rotary evaporation obtains crystals of the final product methamphetamine hydrochloride, which are placed in a vacuum drying oven to dry at room temperature.

上述用于法庭科学毒品检测的甲基苯丙胺标准物质的纯化制备方法，在步骤(2.1)中，首先对甲基苯丙胺样品进行手性分析，并选择只含有单一异构体构型的样品作为制备原料得到相应的异构体标准物质。Above-mentioned purification preparation method for the methamphetamine standard substance that is used for forensic science drug detection, in step (2.1), at first the methamphetamine sample is carried out chiral analysis, and selects the sample that only contains single isomer configuration as preparation The starting material was obtained from the corresponding isomer standard material.

上述用于法庭科学毒品检测的甲基苯丙胺标准物质的纯化制备方法，对甲基苯丙胺样品进行手性分析包括如下步骤：The above-mentioned method for the purification and preparation of the methamphetamine standard substance used for forensic science drug detection, the chiral analysis of the methamphetamine sample comprises the following steps:

(2.1.1)按体积比正己烷：异丙醇：三氟乙酸：二乙胺＝92:8:0.1:0.05配制手性分析用流动相；(2.1.1) n-hexane by volume ratio: isopropanol: trifluoroacetic acid: diethylamine=92:8:0.1:0.05 to prepare the mobile phase for chiral analysis;

(2.1.2)1mg甲基苯丙胺样品溶于5mL萃取溶剂(按体积比甲醇：乙醇：流动相＝2:3:5)，配成质量体积浓度为0.2mg/mL甲基苯丙胺样品溶液用于手性柱液相色谱分析；使用前样品溶液经过0.45μm微孔滤膜过滤；(2.1.2) 1mg methamphetamine sample is dissolved in 5mL extraction solvent (methanol by volume ratio: ethanol: mobile phase=2:3:5), is made into mass volume concentration and is 0.2mg/mL methamphetamine sample solution for use Chiral column liquid chromatography analysis; the sample solution was filtered through a 0.45 μm microporous membrane before use;

(2.1.3)色谱柱为CHIRALCEL OZ-H柱，250mm×4.6mm I.D.，5μm；流动相为正己烷：异丙醇：三氟乙酸：二乙胺＝92:8:0.1:0.05，等度洗脱；紫外检测波长214nm；流速1.0mL/min；柱温35℃；(2.1.3) The chromatographic column is CHIRALCEL OZ-H column, 250mm×4.6mm I.D., 5μm; the mobile phase is n-hexane:isopropanol:trifluoroacetic acid:diethylamine=92:8:0.1:0.05, isocratic Elution; UV detection wavelength 214nm; flow rate 1.0mL/min; column temperature 35°C;

(2.1.4)试验选择的手性柱固定相为表面涂敷了手性多聚物的球形硅胶，手性多聚物为纤维素-三-(3-氯-4-甲基苯基氨基甲酸酯)，甲基苯丙胺的紫外吸收图选择检测波长为214nm。(2.1.4) The chiral column stationary phase selected for the test is spherical silica gel coated with a chiral polymer on the surface, and the chiral polymer is cellulose-tri-(3-chloro-4-methylphenylamino Formic acid ester), the ultraviolet absorption figure selection detection wavelength of methamphetamine is 214nm.

本发明的有益效果如下：The beneficial effects of the present invention are as follows:

本发明制备纯化方法得到的甲基苯丙胺晶体中，按照高效液相色谱峰面积归一化法计算甲基苯丙胺纯度大于或等于99.1wt％。In the methamphetamine crystal obtained by the preparation and purification method of the present invention, the purity of the methamphetamine calculated according to the peak area normalization method of high performance liquid chromatography is greater than or equal to 99.1 wt%.

本发明制备纯化方法得到的甲基苯丙胺经核磁共振、液相色谱-串联质谱联用、红外光谱分析确认，其纯度经液相色谱、气相色谱确认定值，并对色谱无响应杂质进行测定；根据标准物质研制要求，其稳定性、均匀性、定值、总不确定度的估计均符合相关规定，达到预期指标。The methamphetamine obtained by the preparation and purification method of the present invention is confirmed by nuclear magnetic resonance, liquid chromatography-tandem mass spectrometry, and infrared spectrum analysis, and its purity is determined by liquid chromatography and gas chromatography, and the chromatographic non-responsive impurities are measured; According to the requirements for the development of reference materials, the estimation of its stability, uniformity, fixed value, and total uncertainty all meet the relevant regulations and meet the expected indicators.

本发明的制备纯化方法可为我国司法鉴定部门提供量值准确、可溯源的甲基苯丙胺标准物质，填补我国法庭科学领域毒品标准物质空白，以改进分析测量质量，提高定量结果的准确度，最大程度地保证测量结果的有效性。有助于建立法庭科学毒品检测量值溯源体系，有利于实现国内法庭科学毒品检测化学测量方法标准化，实现测量结果的可靠、有效和互认。The preparation and purification method of the present invention can provide my country's judicial appraisal department with accurate and traceable methamphetamine standard substances, fill the blank of drug standard substances in the field of forensic science in my country, improve the quality of analysis and measurement, and improve the accuracy of quantitative results. To ensure the validity of the measurement results to the greatest extent. It is helpful to establish a traceability system for forensic science drug detection quantity, is conducive to the standardization of domestic forensic science drug detection chemical measurement methods, and realizes the reliability, effectiveness and mutual recognition of measurement results.

克服了现有技术制备纯化方法得到的甲基苯丙胺样品存在的纯度低、稳定性差、均匀性差、制备过程复杂等缺陷，提供了一种利用高效液相色谱分离法获得高纯度、高稳定性、回收率高、便于规模化生产的甲基苯丙胺标准物质制备方法。It overcomes the defects of low purity, poor stability, poor uniformity, and complicated preparation process in the methamphetamine samples obtained by the preparation and purification methods of the prior art, and provides a high-purity, high-stability, high-performance liquid chromatography separation method. The invention discloses a method for preparing methamphetamine standard substance which has high recovery rate and is convenient for large-scale production.

二、甲基苯丙胺光学异构体的测定及原料筛选2. Determination of optical isomers of methamphetamine and screening of raw materials

2.1流动相及样品溶液制备2.1 Mobile phase and sample solution preparation

2.1.1手性分析流动相制备2.1.1 Mobile phase preparation for chiral analysis

按体积比正己烷：异丙醇：三氟乙酸：二乙胺＝92:8:0.1:0.05配制手性分析用流动相。The mobile phase for chiral analysis was prepared according to the volume ratio of n-hexane:isopropanol:trifluoroacetic acid:diethylamine=92:8:0.1:0.05.

2.1.2手性分析样品溶液制备2.1.2 Chiral analysis sample solution preparation

1mg甲基苯丙胺样品溶于5mL萃取溶剂(按体积比甲醇：乙醇：流动相＝2:3:5)，配成质量体积浓度为0.2mg/mL甲基苯丙胺样品溶液用于手性柱液相色谱分析。使用前样品溶液经过0.45μm微孔滤膜过滤。1mg methamphetamine sample was dissolved in 5mL extraction solvent (methanol:ethanol:mobile phase=2:3:5 by volume ratio), and the mass volume concentration was made into 0.2mg/mL methamphetamine sample solution for chiral column liquid phase spectrum analysis. The sample solution was filtered through a 0.45 μm microporous membrane before use.

2.2仪器条件2.2 Instrument conditions

色谱柱为CHIRALCEL OZ-H柱(250mm×4.6mm I.D.，5μm)；流动相为正己烷：异丙醇：三氟乙酸：二乙胺＝92:8:0.1:0.05(此处为体积比)，等度洗脱；紫外检测波长214nm；流速1.0mL/min；柱温35℃。The chromatographic column is a CHIRALCEL OZ-H column (250mm×4.6mm I.D., 5 μm); the mobile phase is n-hexane:isopropanol:trifluoroacetic acid:diethylamine=92:8:0.1:0.05 (here is the volume ratio) , isocratic elution; UV detection wavelength 214nm; flow rate 1.0mL/min; column temperature 35°C.

2.3高效液相色谱手性分析条件的建立2.3 Establishment of HPLC chiral analysis conditions

试验选择的手性柱固定相为表面涂敷了手性多聚物(纤维素-三-(3-氯4-甲基苯基氨基甲酸酯)的球形硅胶，具有高分离选择性和广泛的适用范围，对许多手性化合物有很高的手性识别能力，适用于含氨基化合物的手性拆分。另根据手性柱《使用手册》，涂敷型固定相所用的流动相一般为正己烷/异丙醇混合物，本申请中通过对流动相体系、流速等条件的优化，最终选择流动相为正己烷：异丙醇：三氟乙酸：二乙胺＝92:8:0.1:0.05(此处为体积比)，能够将甲基苯丙胺与样品中的杂质分离开，获得了更好的分离效果。根据甲基苯丙胺的紫外吸收图选择检测波长为214nm。The chiral column stationary phase selected in the test is spherical silica gel coated with a chiral polymer (cellulose-tri-(3-chloro-4-methylphenylcarbamate) on the surface, which has high separation selectivity and a wide range of It has a high chiral recognition ability for many chiral compounds and is suitable for the chiral resolution of amino-containing compounds. According to the "Instruction Manual" for chiral columns, the mobile phase used for coating-type stationary phases is generally n-hexane/isopropanol mixture, in this application, through the optimization of mobile phase system, flow rate and other conditions, the final selection of mobile phase is n-hexane:isopropanol:trifluoroacetic acid:diethylamine=92:8:0.1:0.05 (Here is volume ratio), methamphetamine can be separated from the impurity in the sample, obtained better separation effect.Select detection wavelength to be 214nm according to the ultraviolet absorption figure of methamphetamine.

2.4样品的测定2.4 Determination of samples

对2011—2012年度案件缴获的晶体样本用分析型液相色谱进行分析后，选择纯度高于70wt％的238份晶体样本进行手性分析，结果表明，有14份晶体中只含有R(-)methamphetamine，有137份只含有S(+)methamphetamine,R(-)与S(+)共存的晶体样本有87份，说明缴获的晶体样本多数只含有右旋甲基苯丙胺。After analyzing the crystal samples seized in the 2011-2012 case with analytical liquid chromatography, 238 crystal samples with a purity higher than 70wt% were selected for chiral analysis. The results showed that 14 crystal samples only contained R(-) For methamphetamine, 137 crystal samples contained only S(+)methamphetamine, and 87 crystal samples where R(-) and S(+) coexisted, indicating that most of the seized crystal samples only contained dextromethamphetamine.

2.5R(-)-甲基苯丙胺及S(+)-甲基苯丙胺标准物质制备时原料的选择2.5 Selection of raw materials for the preparation of R(-)-methamphetamine and S(+)-methamphetamine standard substances

从原理上，在甲基苯丙胺制备液相色谱分离过程中，如果没有加入手性衍生化试剂或手性催化剂，整个制备过程不会导致异构体空间构型的改变。因此根据我们对案件缴获晶体的手性分析结果，可以选择只含有单一异构体构型的晶体样本作为制备原料得到相应的异构体标准物质。In principle, during the liquid chromatography separation process for the preparation of methamphetamine, if no chiral derivatization reagent or chiral catalyst is added, the entire preparation process will not lead to changes in the spatial configuration of isomers. Therefore, according to the chiral analysis results of the crystals seized in the case, we can choose crystal samples containing only a single isomer configuration as raw materials for preparation to obtain corresponding isomer standard substances.

根据对案件缴获样本的测定结果，选取只含有R(-)-methamphetamine和S(+)-methamphetamine的晶体样本，分别配制成样品溶液，经制备液相色谱分离可得到不同手性的甲基苯丙胺光学异构体。According to the measurement results of the samples seized in the case, crystal samples containing only R(-)-methamphetamine and S(+)-methamphetamine were selected and prepared into sample solutions respectively, and different chiral methamphetamines could be obtained by preparative liquid chromatography separation optical isomers.

3.4高效液相色谱分析条件的优化3.4 Optimization of HPLC analysis conditions

3.4.1色谱柱的选择3.4.1 Selection of chromatographic column

据文献报导，甲基苯丙胺样品的HPLC分析，多采用反相高效液相色谱方法，利用C色谱柱进行分析。由于试验中建立的高效液相色谱分析方法既要适合分析甲基苯丙胺晶体样品，又要有利于后期放大建立高效液相色谱制备方法，因此在色谱柱的选择上综合考虑了色谱柱填料、对应制备柱型号、价格等因素，采用shim-pack HRC-ODS(250mm×4.6mmI.D.，5μm)分析型色谱柱对甲基苯丙胺样品进行分析。According to bibliographical reports, the HPLC analysis of methamphetamine sample adopts the reversed-phase high-performance liquid chromatography method more, utilizes C 18 chromatographic column to analyze. Since the HPLC analysis method established in the experiment should not only be suitable for the analysis of methamphetamine crystal samples, but also be conducive to the later scale-up and establishment of the HPLC preparation method, the selection of the chromatographic column comprehensively considered the column packing, corresponding Preparative column model, price and other factors, using shim-pack HRC-ODS (250mm×4.6mmI.D., 5μm) analytical chromatographic column to analyze methamphetamine samples.

3.4.2检测波长的选择3.4.2 Selection of detection wavelength

以甲醇-0.05％三氟乙酸/水(V：V＝15:85，本申请中0.05％三氟乙酸/水是指三氟乙酸体积分数为0.05％的三氟乙酸水溶液)为流动相，上样体积10μL，样品浓度1mg/mL，流速1.0mL/min，温度为室温，检测波长分别为210nm、215nm、220nm、230nm、235nm、254nm，对甲基苯丙胺样品溶液进行HPLC分析。比较不同检测波长下主成分与杂质响应差异，结果如图1。With methanol-0.05% trifluoroacetic acid/water (V methanol : V 0.05% trifluoroacetic acid/water =15:85, 0.05% trifluoroacetic acid/water in this application refers to trifluoroacetic acid whose volume fraction is 0.05%. Acetic acid aqueous solution) is the mobile phase, the loading volume is 10 μ L, the sample concentration is 1 mg/mL, the flow rate is 1.0 mL/min, the temperature is room temperature, and the detection wavelengths are respectively 210 nm, 215 nm, 220 nm, 230 nm, 235 nm, 254 nm, and p-methamphetamine sample solution HPLC analysis was performed. The difference in response to principal components and impurities at different detection wavelengths was compared, and the results are shown in Figure 1.

由试验结果知，在选定的6个波长条件下，在220nm时，检测出的杂质成分最多，且各杂质成分的响应均较高，其次是254nm、210nm、215nm，在230nm和235nm条件下杂质成分响应最低。结合甲基苯丙胺的最大紫外吸收范围200～220nm(图2)，确定方法的检测波长为220nm。According to the test results, under the selected 6 wavelength conditions, at 220nm, the detected impurity components are the most, and the response of each impurity component is higher, followed by 254nm, 210nm, 215nm, and under the conditions of 230nm and 235nm Impurities have the lowest response. Combined with methamphetamine's maximum ultraviolet absorption range of 200-220nm (Figure 2), the detection wavelength of the determination method is 220nm.

3.4.3流动相体系的选择3.4.3 Selection of mobile phase system

在反相键合相色谱中，通常采用的流动相主体是水，同时加入甲醇、乙腈或四氢呋喃作为改性剂以改善分离的选择性。由于四氢呋喃的紫外吸收波长是220nm，与试验选择的检测波长相同，为避免流动相造成的背景干扰，关于反相液相色谱流动相体系的选择，分别对甲醇-0.05％三氟乙酸(TFA)/水体系、甲醇-0.5％乙酸/水体系(0.5％乙酸/水是指乙酸体积分数为0.5％的乙酸水溶液)、甲醇-水体系、乙腈-水体系以及乙腈-0.05％三氟乙酸(TFA)/水体系进行了考察。In reversed-phase bonded phase chromatography, water is usually used as the main mobile phase, and methanol, acetonitrile or tetrahydrofuran are added as modifiers to improve the selectivity of separation. Since the ultraviolet absorption wavelength of tetrahydrofuran is 220nm, which is the same as the detection wavelength selected by the test, in order to avoid the background interference caused by the mobile phase, regarding the selection of the reversed-phase liquid chromatography mobile phase system, methanol-0.05% trifluoroacetic acid (TFA) /water system, methanol-0.5% acetic acid/water system (0.5% acetic acid/water refers to the acetic acid aqueous solution whose volume fraction of acetic acid is 0.5%), methanol-water system, acetonitrile-water system and acetonitrile-0.05% trifluoroacetic acid (TFA )/water system was investigated.

⑴醇-0.05％三氟乙酸(TFA)/水体系考察⑴Alcohol-0.05% trifluoroacetic acid (TFA)/water system investigation

上样体积10μL，样品浓度1mg/mL，温度为室温，流速1.0mL/min，检测波长220nm，分别以甲醇体积分数为15％、20％、25％、30％和35％的甲醇-0.05％三氟乙酸水溶液为流动相，考察不同甲醇比例时样品中甲基苯丙胺及其相邻杂质峰分离情况。The sample volume is 10 μL, the sample concentration is 1 mg/mL, the temperature is room temperature, the flow rate is 1.0 mL/min, and the detection wavelength is 220 nm. Trifluoroacetic acid aqueous solution was used as the mobile phase, and the separation of methamphetamine and its adjacent impurity peaks in the sample was investigated at different methanol ratios.

由试验知，随着甲醇含量的逐渐增加，流动相极性降低，各杂质峰及甲基苯丙胺的保留时间逐渐提前。在甲醇体积含量为15％和20％(图3、图4)时，虽然相邻杂质峰同甲基苯丙胺色谱峰达到了基线分离，但分析时间较长，超过了40min。30％和35％甲醇含量时，15分钟以内，全部组分被洗脱，甲基苯丙胺与其前面的杂质峰达到了基线分离，但甲醇含量30％时，甲胺与其后面的杂质峰部分重叠(图6)，甲醇含量35％时，后面的杂质峰在甲胺色谱峰上形成一个肩峰(图7)。在25％甲醇含量时(图5)，在30min内全部组分从色谱柱中洗出，甲胺色谱峰同前后杂质峰均达到了基线分离。因此，从试验结果判断，采用甲醇-0.05％三氟乙酸(TFA)/水体系分析甲基苯丙胺样品溶液，25％体积分数甲醇含量时，主成分甲基苯丙胺和相邻杂质成分的分离效果最佳。Know by experiment, along with the gradual increase of methanol content, mobile phase polarity reduces, and the retention time of each impurity peak and methamphetamine advances gradually. When methanol volume content is 15% and 20% (Fig. 3, Fig. 4), although adjacent impurity peak has reached baseline separation with methamphetamine chromatographic peak, analysis time is longer, surpassed 40min. During 30% and 35% methyl alcohol content, within 15 minutes, all components were eluted, methamphetamine and its front impurity peak reached baseline separation, but when methanol content was 30%, methylamine and its back impurity peak partially overlapped ( Fig. 6), when the methanol content is 35%, the impurity peak behind forms a shoulder peak (Fig. 7) on the methylamine chromatographic peak. When the methanol content was 25% (Fig. 5), all the components were washed out from the chromatographic column within 30 min, and the methylamine chromatographic peaks were separated from the front and rear impurity peaks by the baseline. Therefore, judge from test result, adopt methanol-0.05% trifluoroacetic acid (TFA)/water system to analyze methamphetamine sample solution, when 25% volume fraction methanol content, the separating effect of main component methamphetamine and adjacent impurity component is the best good.

上样体积10μL，样品浓度1mg/mL，温度为室温，流速1.0mL/min，检测波长220nm，分别以甲醇体积含量5％、15％、20％、25％甲醇-0.5％乙酸水溶液为流动相，考察不同甲醇比例时样品中甲基苯丙胺及其相邻杂质峰分离情况。The sample volume is 10 μL, the sample concentration is 1 mg/mL, the temperature is room temperature, the flow rate is 1.0 mL/min, and the detection wavelength is 220 nm. The mobile phases are 5%, 15%, 20%, and 25% methanol-0.5% acetic acid aqueous solution by volume respectively. , to investigate the separation of methamphetamine and its adjacent impurity peaks in samples at different methanol ratios.

试验结果表明(图8～图11)，以甲醇-0.5％乙酸水溶液为流动相，检测波长为220nm，在改变甲醇体积含量为5％至25％时，均检测不到杂质峰，原因在于流动相中乙酸在220nm时的紫外吸收导致本底干扰增大，基线噪音增加，使杂质和甲基苯丙胺的检测灵敏度降低。The test result shows (Fig. 8～Fig. 11), with methanol-0.5% acetic acid aqueous solution as mobile phase, detection wavelength is 220nm, when changing methanol volume content to be 5% to 25%, all can not detect impurity peak, reason is that flow The ultraviolet absorption of acetic acid in the phase at 220nm leads to increased background interference and increased baseline noise, which reduces the detection sensitivity of impurities and methamphetamine.

3.4.6高效液相色谱制备条件的优化3.4.6 Optimization of HPLC preparation conditions

3.4.6.1流动相流速的选择3.4.6.1 Selection of mobile phase flow rate

理论上，从分析液相色谱条件转化到制备液相色谱条件，填料相同、柱长相同的情况下，制备型色谱柱的流速可以根据以下公式线性放大。Theoretically, the flow rate of the preparative chromatographic column can be linearly scaled up according to the following formula when the condition of analytical liquid chromatography is converted to the condition of preparative liquid chromatography with the same filler and the same column length.

X＝r /r X＝r 2 2 /r 1 2

其中，X----放大系数Among them, X---magnification factor

r----制备柱半径r 2 ---- preparation column radius

r----分析柱半径r 1 ---- analysis column radius

本试验中分析柱半径为4.6mm，制备柱半径为20mm，若按上述公式计算，放大系数为18.9，则制备柱流量理论计算值为18.9mL/min。但在制备色谱的分离方法建立中，如果流速按理论计算值设定，则色谱柱压力远超过最大压力(20KPa)限制，因此经过试验考察确定流动相流速如下。In this test, the radius of the analytical column is 4.6 mm, and the radius of the preparative column is 20 mm. If calculated according to the above formula, the amplification factor is 18.9, and the theoretically calculated flow rate of the preparative column is 18.9 mL/min. However, in the establishment of the separation method of preparative chromatography, if the flow rate is set according to the theoretical calculation value, the pressure of the chromatographic column will far exceed the maximum pressure (20KPa) limit, so the flow rate of the mobile phase is determined as follows through experimental investigation.

表4：不同流动相体系下流速设定值Table 4: Flow rate settings under different mobile phase systems

3.4.6.2流动相体系的考察3.4.6.2 Investigation of mobile phase system

关于制备液相色谱流动相体系的选择，我们分别对甲醇-0.05％三氟乙酸(TFA)/水(二者体积比25：75)、甲醇-0.5％乙酸/水(二者体积比25：75)、甲醇-水(二者体积比5：95)体系进行了考察。Regarding the selection of the mobile phase system for preparing liquid chromatography, we respectively made methanol-0.05% trifluoroacetic acid (TFA)/water (both volume ratio 25:75), methanol-0.5% acetic acid/water (both volume ratio 25: 75), methanol-water (both volume ratio 5:95) systems were investigated.

采用甲醇-0.05％三氟乙酸/水(二者体积比25:75)体系分离样品中的甲基苯丙胺组分，由试验结果可知(图18)，在分析型高效液相色谱中，甲基苯丙胺能够与样品中的其他杂质组分达到良好分离，但经过制备柱分离后却没有出现与分析柱上类似的谱图，分析柱甲基苯丙胺组分的保留时间为12.15min，制备柱峰开始时间是10min，保留时间提前。同时，分离度降低，色谱峰出现较大扩展，峰开始和峰结束的时间间隔超过10min，杂质峰与甲基苯丙胺色谱峰发生重叠。Adopt methyl alcohol-0.05% trifluoroacetic acid/water (both volume ratio 25:75) system to separate the methamphetamine component in the sample, know (Fig. 18) by test result, in analytical high performance liquid chromatography, methyl Amphetamine can be well separated from other impurity components in the sample, but there is no spectrum similar to that on the analytical column after separation by the preparative column. The retention time of the methamphetamine component on the analytical column is 12.15min, and the peak of the preparative column begins The time is 10 minutes, and the retention time is advanced. Simultaneously, the resolution decreased, the chromatographic peaks expanded greatly, the time interval between peak start and peak end exceeded 10min, and impurity peaks overlapped with methamphetamine chromatographic peaks.

采用甲醇-0.5％乙酸/水体系(25:75)分离样品中的甲基苯丙胺组分，结果从图19可见，与分析型色谱分离结果相比，色谱峰未出现较大扩展，组分保留时间延后，分析柱甲基苯丙胺的出峰时间是5.28min，制备柱上是10.31分钟，峰起始时间间隔约为5min。甲基苯丙胺色谱峰两侧有杂质峰出现，甲基苯丙胺与其前后相邻杂质峰的分离度分别为0.72和0.69。Adopt methanol-0.5% acetic acid/water system (25:75) to separate the methamphetamine component in the sample, the result can be seen from Figure 19, compared with the analytical chromatographic separation results, the chromatographic peak does not appear to expand greatly, and the component retains Time delay, the peak eluting time of methamphetamine on the analytical column is 5.28 minutes, and it is 10.31 minutes on the preparative column, and the peak starting time interval is about 5 minutes. Impurity peaks appeared on both sides of the chromatographic peak of methamphetamine, and the separation degrees of methamphetamine and its adjacent impurity peaks were 0.72 and 0.69, respectively.

采用甲醇-水(二者体积比5:95)体系分离样品中的甲基苯丙胺组分，从得到的色谱图看(图20)，甲醇-水(二者体积比5:95)体系分离效果好于甲醇-0.5％乙酸/水(25:75)体系，甲基苯丙胺色谱峰与其前面相邻杂质峰分离度为1.19。Adopt methanol-water (both volume ratio 5:95) system to separate the methamphetamine component in the sample, see from the obtained chromatogram (Figure 20), methanol-water (both volume ratio 5:95) system separation effect Better than the methanol-0.5% acetic acid/water (25:75) system, the separation between methamphetamine chromatographic peak and its front adjacent impurity peak is 1.19.

综合考虑，如果采用峰重叠法收集馏分，甲醇-0.5％乙酸/水体系(二者体积比25:75)和甲醇-水(5:95)水体系均可以考虑作为流动相分离甲基苯丙胺样品。Considering comprehensively, if the peak overlapping method is used to collect fractions, methanol-0.5% acetic acid/water system (the volume ratio of the two is 25:75) and methanol-water (5:95) water system can be considered as mobile phases for the separation of methamphetamine samples .

3.4.6.3进样量考察及流动相体系确定3.4.6.3 Inspection of injection volume and determination of mobile phase system

通常液相色谱制备是在柱超载的情况下进行，据文献报导，实际应用中在同样上样量时，体积超载对制备分离柱效的影响比质量超载的影响更大，因此在制备型HPLC中，一般采用质量超载的方式。本试验样本浓度为320mg/mL，接近室温条件下样品溶解的饱和状态，分离条件分别选择甲醇-0.5％乙酸/水(二者体积比25：75)体系或甲醇-水(二者体积比5:95)水体系作为流动相，从阈值大于75mAu开始收集馏分，馏分经过分析型液相色谱检测。考察不同流动相体系、不同进样体积时馏分的归一化纯度及回收情况。Usually the preparation of liquid chromatography is carried out under the condition of column overloading. According to literature reports, in practical applications, when the same amount of sample is loaded, volume overloading has a greater impact on preparative separation column efficiency than mass overloading. Therefore, in preparative HPLC In general, the method of mass overloading is adopted. The concentration of the sample in this test is 320mg/mL, which is close to the saturated state of sample dissolution at room temperature. The separation conditions are methanol-0.5% acetic acid/water (both volume ratio 25:75) system or methanol-water (both volume ratio 5 : 95) water system is used as mobile phase, begins to collect cut from threshold greater than 75mAu, and cut is detected through analytical liquid chromatography. The normalized purity and recovery of fractions in different mobile phase systems and different injection volumes were investigated.

表5：不同流动相体系下进样量考察结果Table 5: Inspection results of injection volume under different mobile phase systems

由表5数据可知，采用上述两种流动相体系，收集阈值高于75mAu的馏分，经过分析型高效液相色谱方法检测，馏分的归一化纯度均能达到99.7％以上。It can be seen from the data in Table 5 that, using the above two mobile phase systems, the fractions with a threshold value higher than 75mAu were collected, and the normalized purity of the fractions could reach more than 99.7% after detection by analytical high performance liquid chromatography.

当采用甲醇-0.5％乙酸/水体系进行分离制备时，随着进样量增加，回收率先升后降，100μL进样时回收率达到最高，为80.95％，120μL进样时，虽然进样量增加了20％，但回收率下降并不明显，仅下降了1.64％。而140μL进样时，回收率迅速降低至74.30％。When using methanol-0.5% acetic acid/water system for separation and preparation, as the injection volume increases, the recovery rises first and then decreases, and the recovery rate reaches the highest when the injection is 100 μL, which is 80.95%. When the injection is 120 μL, although the injection volume There was an increase of 20%, but the decline in recovery rate was not obvious, only decreased by 1.64%. When 140μL was injected, the recovery rate decreased rapidly to 74.30%.

采用甲醇-水体系进行分离制备，收集阈值高于75Amu的馏分，不同进样体积时均能获得较高的制备回收率，当进样体积为160μL时，制备回收率最高，达到87.84％。The methanol-water system was used for separation and preparation, and the fraction with a threshold value higher than 75Amu was collected. Higher preparation recoveries could be obtained at different injection volumes. When the injection volume was 160 μL, the preparation recovery was the highest, reaching 87.84%.

综合考虑，确定甲醇-水(二者体积比5:95)体系作为制备液相色谱分离甲基苯丙胺的流动相，进样体积为160μL。Considering comprehensively, the methanol-water (volume ratio of the two is 5:95) system was determined as the mobile phase for the separation of methamphetamine by liquid chromatography, and the injection volume was 160 μL.

3.4.6.4馏分收集范围的确定3.4.6.4 Determination of fraction collection range

采用制备液相色谱分离纯化，可以按保留时间收集馏分，也可根据阈值或色谱峰斜率进行收集。考虑到每次进样保留时间很难完全重合，为避免因保留时间的细微变化而引入杂质，实验中采用按信号阈值收集馏分的方式，分别对阈值高于60mAu，70mAu，75mAu，80mAu，85mAu范围内收集馏分进行HPLC分析，结果表明当阈值高于60mAu即可收集到纯度大于99.5wt％的馏分。最终确定收集信号阈值高于75mAu范围内的馏分。Using preparative liquid chromatography for separation and purification, fractions can be collected according to retention time, or according to threshold or chromatographic peak slope. Considering that the retention time of each injection is difficult to completely overlap, in order to avoid the introduction of impurities due to slight changes in retention time, the method of collecting fractions according to the signal threshold was adopted in the experiment, and the threshold values were higher than 60mAu, 70mAu, 75mAu, 80mAu, 85mAu respectively Fractions were collected within the range for HPLC analysis, and the results showed that fractions with a purity greater than 99.5wt% could be collected when the threshold was higher than 60mAu. Final determination was made to collect fractions with a signal threshold above the range of 75mAu.

3.4.6.5批处理程序3.4.6.5 Batch programs

经过试验考察，在所采用的制备液相色谱条件下，45min内全部组分均能从制备柱中流出，因此在批处理运行过程中我们首先采用流动相中的甲醇和水分别经过A、B泵注入后经制备液相混合进柱。在批处理运行初期分离效果较好，但随后发现，色谱峰出现严重变形，保留时间改变，仪器不能按预先设定的参数收集馏分，经查找原因发现是由于管路中充斥大量气泡导致分离效果降低所致。进一步的试验查明，由于制备分离的流动相体系是由甲醇和水组成，当水与甲醇混合时，将出现放热现象，混合溶剂体积减小，同时有大量气泡释放。因此，试验采用进泵前将甲醇和水(二者体积比5:95)按比例混合，充分混匀脱气后使用。批处理运行可连续进样。After testing and investigation, under the preparative liquid chromatographic conditions adopted, all components can flow out of the preparative column within 45 minutes. Therefore, in the batch operation process, we first use methanol and water in the mobile phase to pass through A and B respectively. After the pump is injected, it is mixed into the column through the preparation liquid phase. The separation effect was good at the beginning of the batch operation, but later it was found that the chromatographic peaks were seriously deformed, the retention time changed, and the instrument could not collect fractions according to the preset parameters. After searching the reason, it was found that the separation effect was caused by a large number of bubbles in the pipeline. caused by the decrease. Further tests have found that since the mobile phase system for preparing separation is composed of methanol and water, when water and methanol are mixed, exothermic phenomenon will occur, the volume of the mixed solvent will decrease, and a large number of bubbles will be released simultaneously. Therefore, the test uses methanol and water (the volume ratio of the two is 5:95) to be mixed in proportion before entering the pump, and then used after fully mixing and degassing. Batch runs allow for continuous injection.

3.4.6.6甲基苯丙胺组分的进一步纯化3.4.6.6 Further purification of the methamphetamine fraction

自动馏分收集器收集制备液相分离后的甲基苯丙胺组分，经减压旋蒸后得到无色透明晶体。通常可用红外光谱法检测得到的透明晶体是否为甲基苯丙胺盐酸盐。也可通过进一步纯化以获得最终的制备产物甲基苯丙胺盐酸盐。试验采用溶剂萃取的方法，分别对pH值、萃取溶剂、萃取溶剂用量、萃取次数等因素进行了考察。结果表明，在pH值大于12条件下，用正己烷萃取，每次萃取时水相与有机相体积比1：1，2次萃取回收率接近100％。The automatic fraction collector collects the methamphetamine components after liquid phase separation, and obtains colorless transparent crystals after rotary evaporation under reduced pressure. Infrared spectroscopy can usually be used to detect whether the obtained transparent crystals are methamphetamine hydrochloride. It can also be further purified to obtain the final product methamphetamine hydrochloride. The method of solvent extraction was adopted in the experiment, and factors such as pH value, extraction solvent, extraction solvent dosage and extraction times were investigated respectively. The results showed that when the pH value was greater than 12, the extraction with n-hexane, the volume ratio of the aqueous phase to the organic phase was 1:1 in each extraction, and the recovery rate of the second extraction was close to 100%.

3.4.6.6.1 pH范围的优化3.4.6.6.1 Optimization of the pH range

收集单针进样的馏分，旋转蒸发去除流动相，残渣用蒸馏水溶解定容至5mL后平行分成5份，每份1mL,分别调节水液的pH值为3、7、9～10、11～12、大于12，各加入1mL正己烷提取，振荡5min，静置分层，移出有机相，余水相分别经HPLC分析，计算不同pH值条件下的萃取回收率。Collect the fractions of single-needle injection, remove the mobile phase by rotary evaporation, dissolve the residue with distilled water to 5mL and divide it into 5 parts in parallel, each 1mL, adjust the pH value of the water solution to 3, 7, 9-10, 11- 12. If it is greater than 12, add 1 mL of n-hexane for extraction, shake for 5 minutes, let stand to separate and separate, remove the organic phase, and analyze the remaining aqueous phase by HPLC, and calculate the extraction recovery under different pH conditions.

表6：不同pH值条件下甲基苯丙胺的萃取回收率Table 6: Extraction recoveries of methamphetamine at different pH values

由表6数据可知，酸性条件下，甲基苯丙胺以成盐的形式溶解在水溶液中，完全不能被正己烷萃取出来。而碱性条件下，甲基苯丙胺以其游离态形式存在，随着pH值的增加，正己烷萃取效率不断提高，在pH大于12条件下，萃取效率最高，达到91.67％。因此确定最佳提取pH值为大于12。It can be seen from the data in Table 6 that under acidic conditions, methamphetamine is dissolved in the aqueous solution in the form of salt, and cannot be extracted by n-hexane at all. Under alkaline conditions, methamphetamine exists in its free form. With the increase of pH value, the extraction efficiency of n-hexane increases continuously. When the pH value is greater than 12, the extraction efficiency is the highest, reaching 91.67%. Therefore, it is determined that the optimum extraction pH value is greater than 12.

3.4.6.6.2提取溶剂的选择3.4.6.6.2 Selection of extraction solvent

收集单针进样的馏分，旋转蒸发去除流动相，残渣用蒸馏水溶解定容至5mL，平行量取4份水液，每份1mL,并调节水液的pH值大于12，向4份水液中分别加入乙酸乙酯、环己烷、氯仿、正己烷，溶剂加入体积均为1mL，振荡10min，离心5min，移出有机相，余水相分别经HPLC分析。计算不同溶剂对甲基苯丙胺的萃取回收率。Collect the fractions of single-needle injection, remove the mobile phase by rotary evaporation, dissolve the residue with distilled water to 5mL, measure 4 parts of water in parallel, each 1mL, and adjust the pH value of the water to be greater than 12, add to 4 parts of water Ethyl acetate, cyclohexane, chloroform, and n-hexane were added to the solution, and the volume of solvent added was 1 mL, shaken for 10 min, centrifuged for 5 min, and the organic phase was removed, and the remaining aqueous phase was analyzed by HPLC. Calculate the extraction recoveries of different solvents for methamphetamine.

表7：pH>12条件下不同溶剂对甲基苯丙胺的萃取回收率Table 7: Extraction recovery of methamphetamine with different solvents under the condition of pH>12

表7中是实验条件下几种溶剂对甲基苯丙胺的萃取回收率值。当pH>12时，各溶剂对甲基苯丙胺的萃取效率依次为正己烷>环己烷>三氯甲烷>乙酸乙酯。因此选择正己烷作为实验的萃取溶剂。Table 7 is the extraction recovery value of several solvents to methamphetamine under the experimental conditions. When the pH>12, the extraction efficiencies of each solvent for methamphetamine were n-hexane>cyclohexane>chloroform>ethyl acetate. Therefore, n-hexane was chosen as the extraction solvent for the experiment.

3.4.6.6.3溶剂用量及萃取次数的选择3.4.6.6.3 Selection of solvent dosage and extraction times

收集单针进样的馏分，旋转蒸发去除流动相，残渣用蒸馏水溶解定容至5mL后平行分成5份，每份1mL,调节溶液的pH值大于12，分别加入正己烷1mL、2mL、3mL、4mL、5mL，振荡10min，离心5min，移出有机相，向水相中再次加入正己烷1mL、2mL、3mL、4mL、5mL进行二次萃取，合并两次提取的有机相，余水相分别经HPLC分析。实验结果见表8。Collect the fractions of single-needle injection, remove the mobile phase by rotary evaporation, dissolve the residue with distilled water to 5mL and divide it into 5 parts in parallel, each 1mL, adjust the pH value of the solution to be greater than 12, add n-hexane 1mL, 2mL, 3mL, 4mL, 5mL, shake for 10min, centrifuge for 5min, remove the organic phase, add 1mL, 2mL, 3mL, 4mL, 5mL of n-hexane to the aqueous phase for secondary extraction, combine the organic phases extracted twice, and the remaining aqueous phases were subjected to HPLC analyze. The experimental results are shown in Table 8.

表8：正己烷用量及萃取次数对甲基苯丙胺萃取回收率结果Table 8: Results of the extraction recovery rate of methamphetamine by the amount of n-hexane and the number of extractions

实验结果表明，一次萃取，随着正己烷与水相体积比的不断增加，萃取效率缓慢提高，当正己烷用量达到水相体积的5倍时，萃取效率达97.8％，仍不能将水液中的甲基苯丙胺完全萃取出来。但二次萃取后，正己烷与水相体积比为1时，萃取效率已达到100％。因此，试验确定萃取时加入与水相相同体积的正己烷，重复萃取两次。The experimental results show that for one extraction, with the continuous increase of the volume ratio of n-hexane and water phase, the extraction efficiency increases slowly. When the amount of n-hexane reaches 5 times the volume of the water phase, the extraction efficiency reaches 97.8%. The methamphetamine is completely extracted. However, after secondary extraction, when the volume ratio of n-hexane to aqueous phase is 1, the extraction efficiency has reached 100%. Therefore, the experiment determined that the same volume of n-hexane as the water phase was added during the extraction, and the extraction was repeated twice.

3.4.6.6.4盐酸溶液加入量的确定3.4.6.6.4 Determination of adding amount of hydrochloric acid solution

采用正己烷萃取后得到的甲基苯丙胺以其原体形式存在于正己烷溶液中，需要进一步试验以得到最终制备产物甲基苯丙胺盐酸盐。试验采用向正己烷溶液中滴加盐酸溶液的方法，对盐酸溶液的加入量进行了考察。The methamphetamine obtained after extraction with n-hexane exists in the n-hexane solution in its original form, and further tests are required to obtain the final product methamphetamine hydrochloride. The test adopts the method of adding hydrochloric acid solution dropwise to n-hexane solution, and the addition amount of hydrochloric acid solution is investigated.

收集单针进样的馏分，旋转蒸发去除流动相，残渣用蒸馏水溶解定容至5mL,调节溶液的pH值大于12，加入正己烷5mL，振荡10min，离心5min，移出有机相，向水相中再次加入正己烷5mL进行二次萃取，合并两次提取的正己烷溶液，并向其中加入5mL水，之后逐滴加入0.01NHCl溶液，采用差减法记录盐酸溶液的用量。Collect fractions from single-needle injection, remove the mobile phase by rotary evaporation, dissolve the residue with distilled water to 5mL, adjust the pH value of the solution to greater than 12, add 5mL of n-hexane, shake for 10min, centrifuge for 5min, remove the organic phase, and pour into the water phase Add 5 mL of n-hexane again for secondary extraction, combine the extracted n-hexane solutions twice, and add 5 mL of water to it, then add 0.01N HCl solution dropwise, and record the amount of hydrochloric acid solution by subtraction method.

实验表明，对于单针进样收集的馏分，经过正己烷萃取后，加入2mL0.01NHCl溶液，水相的pH值可以达到4～5,得到最终制备产物甲基苯丙胺盐酸盐水溶液。Experiments have shown that for the fraction collected by single-needle injection, after extraction with n-hexane, adding 2mL of 0.01N HCl solution, the pH value of the aqueous phase can reach 4-5, and the final product methamphetamine hydrochloride aqueous solution is obtained.

3.4.6.6.5制备产物的干燥3.4.6.6.5 Drying of prepared products

馏分经过正己烷提取并进一步转化成甲基苯丙胺盐酸盐后，可以旋转蒸发去除正己烷，剩余水相经过冷冻干燥或旋转蒸发均可获得最终制备产物甲基苯丙胺盐酸盐晶体。但试验证明，旋转蒸发的加热过程中极易引入杂质，使标准物质的纯度降低，因此为获取高纯度的标准物质，应使用冷冻干燥技术以获取最终的制备产物。同时实验也发现，当盐酸溶液加入过量时，经过干燥后最终获得的制备产物颜色泛黄。After the distillate is extracted with n-hexane and further converted into methamphetamine hydrochloride, the n-hexane can be removed by rotary evaporation, and the remaining water phase can be freeze-dried or rotary-evaporated to obtain crystals of the final product methamphetamine hydrochloride. However, experiments have shown that impurities are easily introduced during the heating process of rotary evaporation, which reduces the purity of standard substances. Therefore, in order to obtain high-purity standard substances, freeze-drying technology should be used to obtain the final preparation. Simultaneously, experiments also found that when the hydrochloric acid solution was added in excess, the color of the final prepared product obtained after drying was yellowish.

冷冻干燥后获得的甲基苯丙胺标准物质通常要经过脱水去除从空气中吸附的水分及残留溶剂，甲基苯丙胺盐酸盐虽然具有很好的热稳定性，标准物质的脱水脱溶剂采用真空干燥箱室温下干燥。The methamphetamine standard substance obtained after freeze-drying usually needs to be dehydrated to remove moisture and residual solvents adsorbed from the air. Although methamphetamine hydrochloride has good thermal stability, the dehydration and desolventization of the standard substance uses a vacuum drying oven. Dry at room temperature.
